                        <tr><td class="num-cell">23</td><td><span class="l4">Hard</span></td><td><span class="lc-link">🔧 Custom</span></td><td class="prob-name">Max Subarray Sum Divisible by K</td><td><span class="diff-h">Hard</span></td><td></td><td class="variant-cell">Kadane's + modular arithmetic + HashMap</td><td class="insight">Prefix sums mod k; same remainder at j and i → sum divisible by k; maximize via earliest HashMap; Hard: modular prefix + Kadane spirit is non-obvious</td></tr>
